title: Biden Knew The Whole Time? (Ep 1836)
description:
In this episode, I address the shocking new allegation that the Biden White House knew in advance about the raid on Trump. I also address an explosive new report about the UFO phenomenon. 

News Picks:


More leaks about the disastrous Mar a Lago raid.


Biden White House facilitated DOJ's criminal probe against Trump, scuttled privilege claims: memos.


The latest congressional action on UFOs will open your eyes.


Working from home is becoming the norm.


Fetterman is a fraud. 

Reports indicate that Biden was personally involved in the attack on Mike Flynn.


A blood test for cancer? I hope this is true.

The NY Times reports on social media company’s efforts to interfere in the coming elections.
